text#{7}":[507,508],"#Building translations#Dynamic text#{8}":[509,512]},"outlinks":[{"title":"`Accept-Language` header","target":"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Accept-Language","line":28},{"title":"column 639-1 in this table","target":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_ISO_639-1_codes","line":28},{"title":"Addendum","target":"./ADDENDUM.md","line":83},{"title":"\n```\n\n#### Locating the node translation file\n\nA node translation file is placed at `/nodes-base/nodes/{node}/translations/{localeIdentifier}`\n\n```\nGitHub\n\t├── GitHub.node.ts\n\t├── GitHubTrigger.node.ts\n\t└── translations\n\t\t└── de\n\t\t\t├── github.json\n\t\t\t└── githubTrigger.json\n```\n\nEvery node must have its own node translation file.\n\n> For information about nodes in **versioned dirs** and **grouping dirs**, refer to the [Addendum","target":"./ADDENDUM.md","line":115},{"title":"Addendum","target":"./ADDENDUM.md","line":459}],"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[[32,35],[39,49],[59,65],[71,73],[98,104],[110,116],[122,130],[138,145],[155,182],[186,193],[209,218],[220,227],[244,258],[260,264],[272,281],[283,289],[301,319],[321,328],[336,342],[350,380],[382,390],[394,439],[441,453],[469,472],[476,480],[490,493],[497,502]]},"smart_blocks:sources/n8n/packages/frontend/@n8n/i18n/docs/README.md#i18n in n8n": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":null},"embeddings":{},"text":null,"length":0,"last_read":{"hash":"tj12mm","at":1782387047111},"key":"sources/n8n/packages/frontend/@n8n/i18n/docs/README.md#i18n in n8n","lines":[1,460],"size":13874,"outlinks":[{"title":"`Accept-Language` header","target":"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Headers/Accept-Language","line":28},{"title":"column 639-1 in this table","target":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_ISO_639-1_codes","line":28},{"title":"Addendum","target":"./ADDENDUM.md","line":83},{"title":"\n```\n\n#### Locating the node translation file\n\nA node translation file is placed at `/nodes-b