"smart_blocks:sources/n8n/packages/frontend/@n8n/i18n/docs/README.md#i18n in n8n#Dynamic text#Locating dynamic text": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":null},"embeddings":{},"text":null,"length":0,"last_read":{"hash":"12geu9a","at":1782387047111},"key":"sources/n8n/packages/frontend/@n8n/i18n/docs/README.md#i18n in n8n#Dynamic text#Locating dynamic text","lines":[92,146],"size":1436,"outlinks":[{"title":"\n```\n\n#### Locating the node translation file\n\nA node translation file is placed at `/nodes-base/nodes/{node}/translations/{localeIdentifier}`\n\n```\nGitHub\n\t├── GitHub.node.ts\n\t├── GitHubTrigger.node.ts\n\t└── translations\n\t\t└── de\n\t\t\t├── github.json\n\t\t\t└── githubTrigger.json\n```\n\nEvery node must have its own node translation file.\n\n> For information about nodes in **versioned dirs** and **grouping dirs**, refer to the [Addendum","target":"./ADDENDUM.md","line":24}],"class_name":"SmartBlock"},
